高等計算機網路




高等計算機網路 (Advanced Computer Networks)

Term: Spring, 2006
Instructor: 陳伶志 Ling-Jyh Chen (cclljj@iis.sinica.edu.tw)
Time: Tuesday 9-12
Room: 1016 Edu. Building
Grading:

In-Class Participation/Discussion: 10%
Homework: 40%
Project: 50% (checkpoint: 10%; project presentation: 15%, project report: 25%) 

Schedule:




